    Stack: same as PR #98 (continuing on the same branch).
    
    What this PR does NOT do (deliberately):
    
      * Does NOT modify PR #93's branch — that's the source-of-truth
        for the baseline; this script just consumes it.
      * Does NOT auto-fetch on platforms other than Mac. The vast
        reviewer (review_pr_k3_feasibility_on_vast.sh) still expects
